title: Ground News - 'Battle-tested' Florida Gulf Coast stuns No. 7 FAU
text:
Summary by Ground News Florida Golf Coast upsets No. 7 Florida Atlantic 72-68, giving the program a huge win. Zach Anderson scored 21 points, Dallion Johnson added 18 and the Eagles beat the Owls. FAU became the highest-ranked opponent FGCU has beaten in its history. Share menu More
